ment club which eventually grew into an investment partnership in the early eighties in  the partnership transformed into monetta financial services inc a registered investment advisory firm in  the flagship monetta fund was launched emphasizing a growth oriented investing philosophy mr bacarella was featured on the cover of kiplinger personal finance magazine highlighting his sell discipline and growth investment philosophy in  the monetta young investor fund was launched combining a passiveactive investment approach the passive portion seeks to minimize performance uncertainty relative to the market while the active portion emphasizes large capitalization growth stocks with a high degree of earnings sustainability and growth in  the founder son robert j bacarella joined the firm and this fatherson team currently comanage the monetta fund and monetta young investor fund relevant links monetta fund young investor fund order investment kit   monetta facts the founder robert s bacarella was featured on the cover of kiplingers finance magazine site links account login order kids financial kit disclosures press releases site map meet our team robert s bacarella founder president and portfolio manager robert j bacarella vice president and portfolio manager keri cronin marketing manager about us map of monetta mutual funds monetta financial services inc a s naperville road suite  wheaton illinois  phone number   email infomonettacom for more information please email us at infomonettacom please read the prospectus carefully before you invest it contains more complete information about the monetta funds including risks specific to each fund fees and expenses a free hardcopy of the prospectus can be obtained by calling  mutual fund investing involves risk principal loss is possible the funds may make shortterm investments without limitation for defensive purposes which investments may provide lower returns than other types of investments the portion of the young investor fun